{"tid":1560103,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳茂波：反修例運動沒影響香港競爭力","createTime":"2019-09-11T05:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T06:46:26.000Z","uid":144372,"like":20,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"8385db8fde8ffa9677c966b79e1469df26c02990","tid":1560103,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:40:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/陳茂波稱過去數月示威活動沒有影響香港核心競爭力-050751689.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E6%95%B8%E6%9C%88%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%8A%9B-050751689.html&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWSL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=3f6ab54b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/陳茂波稱過去數月示威活動沒有影響香港核心競爭力-050751689.html</a><br />\n<br />\n 財政司司長陳茂波在一帶一路高峰論壇致辭時表示，過去數月示威活動，反映複雜議題，但他保證沒有影響香港核心競爭力，包括法治、表達自由、簡單低稅制、獨立司法制度，以及資本、貨物、資訊及人員的自由流動。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波又認為，一國兩制亦沒有因為近期社會狀況受損，特區政府將與社會對話，希望找出解決方法，配合本港的法治，相信香港會渡過難關。"},{"pid":"44ef8b248701daae9de64b63eed564fdb5dacd90","tid":1560103,"uid":92453,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:41:48.000Z","msg":"你講就係架喇咩柒頭"},{"pid":"07f7b5bad62ed6b0d8a3e2b12e35aee0d6934f47","tid":1560103,"uid":244417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:42:20.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"9954dd40ba0ea9824a63c2026a9fbc48a3fe625b","tid":1560103,"uid":278946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:42:22.000Z","msg":"一時一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be6c10733d318c3573dddfcff0677270d2c06a9","tid":1560103,"uid":44171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:42:25.000Z","msg":"